WEBVTT

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:33.182
They would come with a hand
or a leg missing,

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:34.886
blood everywhere.

00:05:35.480 --> 00:05:39.394
They would sit quietly
wherever they found space

00:05:39.800 --> 00:05:42.698
and would wait for the doctor to get free.

00:05:43.200 --> 00:05:46.073
Somebody had just buried a child,

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:49.016
someone's home had just been bombed.

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:53.679
Yet nobody was crying or screaming.

00:05:54.200 --> 00:05:57.560
At the age of 70 I learnt "respect."

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:00.878
My South Sudanese patients,